metadata.name: Master Yoda | CryptoBeavers.club by PKatzenberger
metadata.description:
*“Do or do not. There is no try.“*


**Master Yoda** | [CryptoBeavers.club](https://cryptobeavers.club) | S-Wars Icons Art Series
by [Philipp Katzenberger](https://philippkatzenberger.de/arbeiten/)
 

---
 
Yoda has always been my favorite. Where most others preferred Vader or Luke, I was fascinated by this wise and powerful creature. Seemingly unimportant and small, Yoda in my eyes is the ultimate underdog that works in the background and enables the Jedi to take their stand.
This is why I have chosen this unlikely hero as my #1, my first NFT ever.

    *Philipp Katzenberger*
 

---
 
**Bonus content**: 
High quality artist-signed art print [claimable](https://philippkatzenberger.de) by the first owner
	
**Artwork specs**:
3000 x 3000 px
Origin 2016-2022 Germany
#1 of 1 pieces, #1 of 50 in [CryptoBeavers.club](https://cryptobeavers.club) series
